   <head>AN ADVERTISEMENT TO THE READER.</head>
   <p>THe Reader may please to take notice, that in the former Edition there was added vnto this Discourse, a iust Volume of aboue three hundred Contradictions and dissentions of the Ro<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>mish Doctors, vnder the name of <hi>The Peace of Rome;</hi> which because it was but a collection out of <hi>Bellarmine</hi> and <hi>Navar,</hi> and no otherwise mine, but as a Gatherer and Translator, I haue here thought good to omit.</p>
</div>
